r /> <strong>2.“天使岩”</strong><br /> <strong>3.“今天”</strong><br /> <strong>4.“解除武装”</strong><br /> <strong>5.《太空男孩》</strong><br /> <strong>6.“间隔”</strong><br /> <strong>7.“蛋黄酱”</strong><br /> <strong>8.“悍马”</strong><br /> <strong>9.“露娜”</strong><br /> <strong>10.“咕噜咕噜”</strong></p><p>在 Smashing Pumpkins 的其他新闻中，今年早些时候，Corgan 透露，他曾经告诉<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pantera">Pantera</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billy-corgan-on-telling-pantera-to-shut-the-fuck-up-about-metallica-3457548">“他妈的闭嘴”，</a>开始质疑<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/metallica">Metallica</a> 。</p><p> “他们只是不停地谈论Metallica。不是消极的方式，而是更困惑，比如，‘我喜欢 Metallica，但我不明白，它们不是金属，这是怎么回事？’，”他解释道。</p><p> “我很了解他们，他们会听我的，我说‘你知道吗？他妈的闭嘴……你们现在是这个星球上最好的金属乐队，好吗？你只需专注于 Pantera 即可。你只需要专注于成为这个星球上最伟大的金属乐队。 Metallica 会解决这个问题的。”他们确实这么做了，对吧？”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-smashing-pumpkins-play-rarities-while-re-staging-siamese-dream-release-show-3500306">《Watch Smashing Pumpkins》在重新上演“Siamese Dream”发行秀时播放稀有节目后，</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
莱斯利·琼斯说，克里斯·洛克在威尔·史密斯获得奥斯卡奖后寻求咨询https://www.nme.com/news/film/chris-rock-sought-coun sell-after-will-smith-oscars-slap-says-leslie-jones-3500298?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=chris-rock-备受追捧的威尔·史密斯奥斯卡奖的咨询顾问莱斯利·琼斯Adam StarkeyTue, 19 Sep 2023 10:32:46 +0000 Film NewsNewsTV NewsOscars https://www.nme.com/?p=3500298 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Chris-Rock-main-new.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="克里斯·洛克" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Chris-Rock-main-new.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Chris-Rock-main-new-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Chris-Rock-main-new-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Chris-Rock-main-new-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Chris-Rock-main-new-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Chris-Rock-main-new-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位喜剧演员的老朋友莱斯利·琼斯表示，这一事件“确实影响了他”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/chris-rock-sought-counselling-after-will-smith-oscars-slap-says-leslie-jones-3500298">克里斯·洛克在威尔·史密斯获得奥斯卡奖后寻求咨询的帖子称莱斯利·琼斯</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Chris-Rock-main-new.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="克里斯·洛克" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Chris-Rock-main-new.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Chris-Rock-main-new-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Chris-Rock-main-new-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Chris-Rock-main-new-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Chris-Rock-main-new-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Chris-Rock-main-new-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>莱斯利·琼斯表示，她的朋友<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chris-rock">克里斯·洛克</a>在 2022 年<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/oscars">奥斯卡颁奖</a>典礼上被<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/will-smith">威尔·史密斯</a>扇耳光后寻求咨询。</p><p>琼斯在接受<a href="https://people.com/leslie-jones-says-will-smith-oscars-slap-really-affected-chris-rock-it-was-humiliating-exclusive-7969431" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《人物》杂志</em></a>采访时宣传她的回忆录（该回忆录的前言是由洛克写的），她说：“这真是令人羞辱。这确实影响了他。人们需要理解他的女儿、他的父母看到了这一点。他必须和他的女儿们一起去接受咨询。”</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><b>阅读更多：</b> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-features/will-smith-chris-rock-relationship-through-the-years-3193434"><b>《Slapgate》的故事：威尔·史密斯和克里斯·洛克多年来的关系</b></a></li></ul><p>琼斯自上世纪 90 年代中期以来一直是洛克的朋友，她说她对奥斯卡的掌掴感到“愤怒”，并补充道：“你不知道我会跳进车里，然后滚到那里。我在很多层面上都他妈的生气了。”</p><p> “克里斯·洛克开了个该死的玩笑，”琼斯继续说道。 “我也认识威尔……我当时想，事后你就无法处理那件事了。这就是奥斯卡奖。全世界都在关注。” </p><figure id="attachment_3500307" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3500307" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3500307" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Chris-Rock-Leslie-Jones-main.jpg" alt="克里斯·洛克 莱斯利·琼斯" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Chris-Rock-Leslie-Jones-main.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Chris-Rock-Leslie-Jones-main-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Chris-Rock-Leslie-Jones-main-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Chris-Rock-Leslie-Jones-main-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Chris-Rock-Leslie-Jones-main-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Chris-Rock-Leslie-Jones-main-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3500307" class="wp-caption-text">莱斯利·琼斯和克里斯·洛克。图片来源：Jim McIsaac/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>在 2022 年 3 月的奥斯卡颁奖典礼上，喜剧演员贾达·萍克特·史密斯 (Jada Pinkett Smith) 开玩笑后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/will-smith-confronts-chris-rock-over-jada-pinkett-smith-joke-at-oscars-2022-3191627">史密斯在台上扇了洛克一</a>巴掌。事件发生后，史密斯向洛克道歉， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/will-smith-has-resigned-from-the-academy-says-he-will-accept-any-further-consequences-3196231">辞去学院职务</a>，并被<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/will-smith-banned-from-oscars-for-10-years-following-slap-3201437">禁止参加学院活动</a>10年。</p><p>史密斯<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/will-smith-posts-emotional-apology-video-to-chris-rock-for-oscars-slap-3279832">后来于 2022 年 7 月在 YouTube 上发布了另一次道歉</a>，他称自己的行为“不可接受”，并补充道：“我只是没有意识到，我没有考虑那一刻有多少人受伤。”</p><p>西恩·潘<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/sean-penn-criticises-actors-response-will-smith-oscars-slap-3498097">最近批评了他的演员同事们对这一耳光的反应</a>，质疑为什么他的同事们站起来为<em>史密斯在当晚晚些时候凭借《理查王》</em>赢得最佳男主角而鼓掌。</p><p> “我不认识威尔·史密斯。我见过他一次，”佩恩告诉<a href="https://variety.com/2023/film/features/sean-penn-slams-will-smith-slap-ai-oscars-1235720417/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《综艺》杂志</em></a>。 “当我见到他时，他看起来很好。他在<em>《理查王》</em>里演得真他妈好。那么你他妈的为什么要用这个愚蠢的东西向自己和其他人吐口水呢？”</p><p>谈到 1987 年因殴打一名男子而入狱的经历，佩恩补充道：“我为什么要因为你刚才的所作所为而进监狱？而你还坐在那里？你们为什么站着为他作为一个人最糟糕的时刻鼓掌？”</p><p>事件发生后，洛克在各种单口秀中拿奥斯卡掌掴开玩笑，其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/chris-rock-jokes-about-will-smith-slap-as-he-joins-dave-chappelle-on-stage-3220295">与戴夫·查佩尔的一场表演</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/chris-rock-sought-counselling-after-will-smith-oscars-slap-says-leslie-jones-3500298">克里斯·洛克在威尔·史密斯获得奥斯卡奖后寻求咨询的帖子称莱斯利·琼斯</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
玛丽莲·曼森因向摄影师擤鼻涕和吐口水而被罚款https://www.nme.com/news/music/marilyn-manson-fined-for-blowing-his-nose-spitting-at-videographer-3500161?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=marilyn-manson-fined-for-向摄像师擤鼻涕吐口水Charlotte KrolTue, 19 Sep 2023 10:08:14 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3500161 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Marilyn-Manson-2000x1270-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="玛丽莲·曼森" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Marilyn-Manson-2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Marilyn-Manson-2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Marilyn-Manson-2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Marilyn-Manson-2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Marilyn-Manson-2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Marilyn-Manson-2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>他对轻罪、简单袭击指控没有提出抗辩</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/marilyn-manson-fined-for-blowing-his-nose-spitting-at-videographer-3500161">玛丽莲·曼森因擤鼻涕和向摄影师吐口水而被罚款的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Marilyn-Manson-2000x1270-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="玛丽莲·曼森" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Marilyn-Manson-2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Marilyn-Manson-2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Marilyn-Manson-2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Marilyn-Manson-2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Marilyn-Manson-2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Marilyn-Manson-2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/marilyn-manson">玛丽莲·曼森 (Marilyn Manson)</a>因<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/marilyn-manson-to-plead-no-contest-in-spitting-and-nose-blowing-assault-case-3471223">涉嫌在 2019 年的一场音乐会上擤鼻涕并向摄像师吐口水</a>而被罚款并被判处 20 小时社区服务。</p><p>据<a href="https://www.wmur.com/article/marilyn-manson-new-hampshire-charge-video/45189197#" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>WMUR</em></a>报道（通过<a href="https://blabbermouth.net/news/marilyn-manson-gets-fine-community-service-for-blowing-nose-on-videographer-in-new-hampshire" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Blabbermouth</em></a> ），这位音乐家昨天（9 月 18 日）出现在新罕布什尔州的法庭上，并对轻罪、简单袭击指控不提出抗辩。这意味着他没有对指控提出异议，也没有认罪。</p><p>曼森的真名是布莱恩·华纳 (Brian Warner)，一名摄影师指控曼森于 2019 年 8 月 19 日在新罕布什尔州吉尔福德的新罕布什尔银行馆向她吐口水和擤鼻涕，因此被指控犯有两项简单袭击轻罪。这是与罗布·赞比 (Rob Zombie) 共同领衔的“地狱不死”巡演的一部分。</p><p>据曼森的律师称，第二项指控已通过协商达成认罪协议而被驳回。曼森将被处以 1,200 美元（969 英镑）的罚款，并被判处 6 个月内完成 20 小时的社区服务。</p><p>这一认罪意味着曼森避免出庭受审。 </p><figure id="attachment_3471228" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3471228" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3471228" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Marilyn-manson-staring.jpg" alt="玛丽莲·曼森于 2020 年 1 月 4 日出席极乐世界艺术第 13 届年度庆典 - 天堂。图片来源：Leon Bennett/GETTY" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Marilyn-manson-staring.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Marilyn-manson-staring-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Marilyn-manson-staring-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Marilyn-manson-staring-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Marilyn-manson-staring-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Marilyn-manson-staring-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3471228" class="wp-caption-text">玛丽莲·曼森于 2020 年 1 月 4 日出席极乐世界艺术第 13 届年度庆典——天堂。图片来源：Leon Bennett/GETTY</figcaption></figure><p>据称，曼森走近摄像师，将脸靠近摄像机，并向她吐了一口“大酒”。这名专业人士的双手被唾液击中。据称，这名音乐家随后第二次回来，捂住一侧鼻孔并向摄像师的方向吹气。</p><p>受害者的辩护律师在法庭上代表摄像师宣读了受害者影响声明。</p><p>声明中写道：“对我来说，我是一名专业人士，我已经在这个行业工作了 30 年。”</p><p> “我曾在很多公司工作过，在我与人共事的这些年里，我从未受到过像这位被告那样的羞辱或对待。他向我吐口水、向我擤鼻涕是人类做过的最恶心的事情。</p><p> “我知道这本来就不是什么大的刑事指控，但我希望被告得到的判决能让他在再次做出类似的事情之前三思而后行。”</p><p>曼森的律师霍华德·金在此前的一份声明中表示：“对于任何参加过玛丽莲·曼森演唱会的人来说，这都不是秘密，他喜欢在舞台上挑衅，尤其是在镜头前。</p><p> “在我们收到一名场地摄像师的手臂上沾染了少量口水后提出的超过 35,000 美元的索赔后，我们提出了这一轻罪索赔。在我们要求提供任何所谓损坏的证据后，我们从未收到答复。整个说法很荒谬，但我们仍然致力于与当局合作，就像我们自始至终所做的那样。”</p><p>曼森最近面临<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/evan-rachel-wood-and-other-women-make-allegations-of-abuse-against-marilyn-manson-2869492">着十几名女性提出的各种诉讼和指控，</a>指控他性虐待和身体虐待。在他否认这些指控后，这位创作型歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/marilyn-manson-dropped-by-record-label-amid-abuse-allegations-2869945">被他的唱片公司 Loma Vista 解雇了</a>。</p><p>其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/westworld"><em>《西部世界》</em></a>演员埃文·雷切尔·伍德，他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/evan-rachel-wood-and-other-women-make-allegations-of-abuse-against-marilyn-manson-2869492">在 2022 年指控曼森诱骗、操纵和“可怕的虐待行为”</a> 。</p><p>目前，这位“Dope Show”歌手还面临着另外两起诉讼，均由简·杜斯提起。他一贯<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/marilyn-manson-denies-abuse-allegations-calls-recent-claims-horrible-distortions-of-reality-2870187">否认所有指控</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/marilyn-manson-fined-for-blowing-his-nose-spitting-at-videographer-3500161">玛丽莲·曼森因擤鼻涕和向摄影师吐口水而被罚款的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
诺埃尔·加拉格尔录制了一首秘密舞曲https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallagher-has-recorded-a-secret-dance-track-3500259?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=noel-gallagher-has-recorded-a-secret-舞曲Charlotte KrolTue, 19 Sep 2023 10:05:11 +0000 Music NewsNewsdanceElectronicIndieRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3500259 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Noel-Gallagher-2000x1270-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="诺埃尔·加拉格尔" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Noel-Gallagher-2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Noel-Gallagher-2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Noel-Gallagher-2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Noel-Gallagher-2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Noel-Gallagher-2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Noel-Gallagher-2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这首歌“听起来就像披头士乐队去印度时一样”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallagher-has-recorded-a-secret-dance-track-3500259">Noel Gallagher 录制的一首秘密舞曲的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Noel-Gallagher-2000x1270-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="诺埃尔·加拉格尔" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Noel-Gallagher-2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Noel-Gallagher-2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Noel-Gallagher-2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Noel-Gallagher-2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Noel-Gallagher-2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Noel-Gallagher-2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noel-gallagher">Noel Gallagher</a>与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/camelphat">CamelPhat</a>录制了一首秘密舞曲，目前正在等待完成。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/noel-gallaghers-high-flying-birds-council-skies-review-3450645">诺埃尔·加拉格尔 (Noel Gallagher) 的《高空飞翔的鸟》——“议会天空”评论：比以前更明亮</a></strong></li></ul><p>CamelPhat DJ 和制作人戴夫·惠兰 (Dave Whelan) 向<a href="https://www.dailystar.co.uk/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《每日星报</em></a><a href="https://www.music-news.com/news/UK/164607/Like-when-The-Beatles-went-to-India-Noel-Gallagher-has-recorded-secret-dance-track" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>》</em></a>的《连线》专栏证实，这对舞蹈组合已与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noel-gallaghers-high-flying-birds">High Flying Birds</a>乐队领队再次合作创作一首歌曲。他们此前曾与这位前 Oasis 明星合作制作了 2020 年的歌曲《Not Over Yet》。</p><p> “我们还与诺埃尔合作创作了一首很棒的歌曲，听起来就像<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-beatles">甲壳虫乐队</a>去印度时一样，”惠兰说。 “它的特色是我们与一位非常有才华的以色列音乐家一起录制的西塔琴。”</p><p>据说加拉格尔忙于制作他的 2023 年专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/noel-gallaghers-high-flying-birds-council-skies-review-3450645">Council Skies</a> 》，无法完成这首歌曲，该歌曲原本打算收录在 CamelPhat 的新专辑《Spiritual Milk》中。 </p><figure id="attachment_2600308" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-2600308" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-2600308" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Camelphat-Press-Image.jpg" alt="骆驼发" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Camelphat-Press-Image.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Camelphat-Press-Image-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Camelphat-Press-Image-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Camelphat-Press-Image-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Camelphat-Press-Image-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Camelphat-Press-Image-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-2600308" class="wp-caption-text"> CamelPhat（图片：媒体）</figcaption></figure><p>惠兰补充道：“诺埃尔的声音并不完整。如果我们邀请另一位歌手来完成这首歌曲，他会很高兴，我们也尝试了。我们使用了五位不同的歌手，但只有诺埃尔的声音听起来不错。目前，赛道就在那里。</p><p> “如果诺埃尔想为他自己的音乐完成它，或者如果他为我们完成它，我们会很高兴 - 无论如何，我们都会尊重诺埃尔的决定。”</p><p>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/coronavirus">新冠疫情</a>封锁期间，Gallager 做出了罕见的举动，与其他几位艺术家合作创作新音乐， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallagher-and-dizzee-rascal-have-worked-on-a-new-track-together-2775386">包括与 Dizzee Rascal</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/imelda-may-just-one-kiss-video-noel-gallagher-ronnie-wood-2866793">Imelda May</a>的合作。</p><p>加拉格尔于 2021 年 5 月接受<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/bbc-radio-6-music">BBC 广播 6 音乐频道</a>采访，谈论了他在禁闭期间的合作。 “讽刺的是，我与他人共同创作了很多歌曲，但似乎没有一首能问世，”他说。</p><p> “我用 CamelPhat 做了那件事，它确实问世了，我用 Dizzee 做了那件事，但从未出现过。我和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paul-weller">[保罗]韦勒</a>做了一件从未完成的事情。事实上，我确实和伊梅尔达·梅做了一些事情，结果确实出来了。</p><p> “很多人都在这样做，我收到很多电子邮件说，‘嘿，我没什么可做的，如果你没什么可做的，我们应该写点东西。’”</p><p>与此同时， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallagher-on-the-prospect-of-a-las-vegas-residency-3497574">加拉格尔最近表示，当他不再巡演时，他将在“晚年”接受拉斯维加斯驻场演出</a>。</p><p>这位音乐家在作为<em>马特·摩根播客的</em>嘉宾出现时说：“我会在维加斯表演诺埃尔·加拉格尔的《高飞的鸟儿》吗？可能在以后的生活中。你不必去任何地方。你住在你玩的酒店里。”</p><p>他继续说道：“<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/elvis-presley">埃尔维斯·普雷斯利</a>过去常常乘坐电梯从他的房间到舞台——我不介意这样做。”</p><p>尽管加拉格尔在拉斯维加斯驻场演出的前景还需要一段时间，但这位音乐家表示，他将 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/u2-announce-las-vegas-residency-during-super-bowl-3397267">在巡演休息期间前往该州度假，观看爱尔兰偶像 U2 的驻场演出</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallagher-has-recorded-a-secret-dance-track-3500259">Noel Gallagher 录制的一首秘密舞曲的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
安德鲁·萨克斯的孙女回应拉塞尔·布兰德性侵犯指控https://www.nme.com/news/tv/andrew-sachs-granddaughter-georgina-baillie-responds-russell-brand-allegations-3500203?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=andrew-sachs-granddaughter-georgina-baillie- responds-russell-brand-allegationsAdam Starkey Tue, 19 Sep 2023 09:45:01 +0000 NewsTV News https://www.nme.com/?p=3500203 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Georgina-Baillie-Russell-Brand.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Georgina Baillie Russell Brand" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Georgina-Baillie-Russell-Brand.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Georgina-Baillie-Russell-Brand-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Georgina-Baillie-Russell-Brand-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Georgina-Baillie-Russell-Brand-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Georgina-Baillie-Russell-Brand-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Georgina-Baillie-Russell-Brand-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “I, from my own personal experience, do not see Russell as a rapist”</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/andrew-sachs-granddaughter-georgina-baillie-responds-russell-brand-allegations-3500203">Andrew Sachs&#39; granddaughter responds to Russell Brand sexual assault allegations</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Georgina-Baillie-Russell-Brand.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Georgina Baillie Russell Brand" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Georgina-Baillie-Russell-Brand.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Georgina-Baillie-Russell-Brand-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Georgina-Baillie-Russell-Brand-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Georgina-Baillie-Russell-Brand-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Georgina-Baillie-Russell-Brand-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Georgina-Baillie-Russell-Brand-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Andrew Sachs&#39; granddaughter Georgina Baillie, who had a relationship with Russell Brand in the 2000s, has addressed the sexual assault allegations against the comedian.</p><p> In a joint investigation by <em>The Sunday Times</em> , <em>The Times</em> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/channel-4">Channel 4&#39;s</a> <em>Dispatches</em> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/russell-brand-accused-of-rape-sexual-assault-and-emotional-abuse-3498938">four women accused Brand of rape and sexual assault</a> over a period between 2006 and 2013. Brand has denied the allegations.</p><p> Baillie was at the centre of the “Sachsgate” scandal in 2008 that saw Brand and TV presenter Jonathan Ross leave a series of “lewd” messages on Sachs&#39; answering machine relating to the comedian&#39;s relationship with his granddaughter. The incident led Brand to resign from the <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/bbc">BBC</a> , while Ross was suspended for 12 weeks.</p><p> In an appearance on TalkTV&#39;s <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@PiersMorganUncensored" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Piers Morgan Uncensored</em></a> yesterday (September 18), Baillie said that she was keeping an “open mind” with regards to the allegations.</p><p> “I&#39;m not saying they are lies because you know, it was a long time ago,” Baillie said. “We all…I think they should be believed and get some help.”</p><p> Asked if she believes there&#39;s any merit to the allegations, she replied: “I, from my own personal experience, do not see Russell as a rapist. However, a lot of the evidence is very compelling, so one has to keep an open mind.”</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"> &quot;I, from my own personal experience, do not see Russell as a rapist.&quot;</p><p> Andrew Sach&#39;s granddaughter Georgina Baillie, who was at the centre of Russell Brand&#39;s infamous &#39;Sachsgate&#39; scandal in 2008, reacts to the allegations made against him. <a href="https://twitter.com/piersmorgan?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@piersmorgan</a> | <a href="https://twitter.com/TalkTV?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@TalkTV</a> | <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/PMU?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#PMU</a> <a href="https://t.co/a77HUuNdQ5">pic.twitter.com/a77HUuNdQ5</a></p><p> — Piers Morgan Uncensored (@PiersUncensored) <a href="https://twitter.com/PiersUncensored/status/1703856598920110273?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">September 18, 2023</a> </p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p> Speaking about her own relationship with Brand, Baillie said: “He was always very nice to me. It was always clear what the parameters were and that was mutually agreed upon and never did anything untoward happen – apart from that [&#39;Sachsgate&#39;].</p><p> “I was struggling with addiction for about 10-15 years and I was finding it very hard to get clean and sober. So one of my mutual friends between me and Russell called him up and said, &#39;Georgie needs some help&#39;, and so he sent me to rehab.</p><p> “And so I was physically separated from my drug of choice and I got some therapy and I think that had a big part to play in my recovery journey.”</p><p> In a <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/russell-brand-posts-video-denying-unspecified-serious-criminal-allegations-3498867">video denying the allegations</a> , Brand said that all of his relationships were consensual.</p><p> “Amidst this litany of astonishing, rather baroque attacks are some very serious allegations that I absolutely refute,” he said. “These allegations pertain to the time when I was working in the mainstream, when I was in the newspapers all the time, when I was in the movies, and as I have written about extensively in my books, I was very, very promiscuous.</p><p> “Now during that time of promiscuity the relationships I had were absolutely, always consensual. I was always transparent about that then, almost too transparent, and I am being transparent about it now as well. To see that transparency metastasised into something criminal, that I absolutely deny, makes me question – is there another agenda at play?”</p><p> Channel 4 and the BBC have both opened investigations into Brand. The former has also <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/russell-brand-episodes-removed-channel-4-website-allegations-3499645">removed all content featuring the comedian</a> from its streaming service.</p><p> <strong>For help, advice or more information regarding sexual harassment, assault and rape in the UK, visit the <a href="https://rapecrisis.org.uk/find-a-centre/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Rape Crisis charity website</a> . In the US, visit <a href="https://www.rainn.org/index.php" target="_blank" rel="noopener">RAINN</a> .</strong></p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/andrew-sachs-granddaughter-georgina-baillie-responds-russell-brand-allegations-3500203">Andrew Sachs&#39; granddaughter responds to Russell Brand sexual assault allegations</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
